neureka.backend.main.implementations.fun

Class ScalarGaSU

  • java.lang.Object
    • neureka.backend.main.implementations.fun.ScalarGaSU
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScalarFun

    public class ScalarGaSU
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScalarFun
    The Self Gated ScalarSoftsign Unit is based on the ScalarSoftsign function (a computationally cheap non-exponential quasi ScalarTanh) making it a polynomially based version of the ScalarGaTU function which is itself based on the ScalarTanh function. Similar as the ScalarSoftsign and ScalarTanh function ScalarGaSU is 0 centered and capped by -1 and +1.
